Trailing spaces are not being stripped off from some of the tested fields, such as {{Security Level}} names and custom field values of type {{select list}}.

This could cause a problem when a project is imported into a target JIRA instance. Similar errors could be experienced:
{quote}
The custom field 'Team' requires option 'eBusiness Architecture ' for the import but it does not exist in the current JIRA instance.
The custom field 'Team' requires option 'eBusiness BAs ' for the import but it does not exist in the current JIRA instance.
The custom field 'Team' requires option 'eBusiness DBAs ' for the import but it does not exist in the current JIRA instance.
The custom field 'Team' requires option 'eBusiness Operations ' for the import but it does not exist in the current JIRA instance.
{quote}
Please note that all the option values above have a trailing space.

